articles.author: Peter Bradshaw
articles.title: Jeanne du Barry review – Cannes kicks off with Johnny Depp’s purring and peculiar royal dandy - The Guardian
articles.description: Louis XV’s infatuation with a sexy, smart courtesan played by Maïwenn – who also writes and directs – is an entertaining spectacle but preening Depp’s king overshadows her story
articles.content: The rosebud lips of Johnny Depp in this film are pursed in a strange expression of irony, stupefied entitlement and droll, martyred awareness of the absurdity of which his royal person is the centre:… [+8872 chars]
